# TradingAgents live monitor — automatic HTTPS via Let's Encrypt.
#
# Deployed on the Hetzner VPS at /etc/caddy/Caddyfile (apt-installed Caddy,
# systemd unit `caddy.service`). The hostname below is a nip.io wildcard
# that resolves to the VPS IP with no DNS setup — Let's Encrypt still issues
# a real trusted cert for it. Swap in an owned domain here if desired.
#
# Prerequisites on the VPS: ufw allow 80/tcp and 443/tcp; ta-monitor.service
# listening on 127.0.0.1:8800.
46.225.169.184.nip.io {
    encode gzip
    reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8800
}
